OL,3,CMan in court charged with murdering
OL,4,Cone-month-old baby son
OL,6,FA man has appeared before court
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of his infant
OL,8,Fson six years ago.
OL,10,FNiall Worsfold is accused of murdering
OL,11,Fthe one-month-old, who died in
OL,12,Fhospital in July 2020.
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police said the child,
OL,15,Fwhose name has not been released, was
OL,16,Fbrought into hospital on 4 July from a
OL,17,Fhouse on Lincombe Drive in Gledhow,
OL,18,FLeeds.
OL,20,FThe baby died in hospital six days
OL,21,Flater on 10 July.
