OL,3,CMan in court charged with murdering
OL,4,Cone-month-old baby son
OL,6,FWorsfold, 29, of Farrow Road, Leeds,
OL,7,Fappeared before Leeds Magistrates
OL,8,FCourt on Thursday charged with murder
OL,9,Fand a count of child cruelty.
OL,11,FHe was remanded into custody and is
OL,12,Fdue to appear before Leeds Crown Court
OL,13,Fon Monday.
OL,15,FPolice on Wednesday said a 25-year-old
OL,16,Fwoman who was investigated by their
OL,17,FHomicide and Major Enquiry Team in
OL,18,Frelation to the baby's death had since
OL,19,Fbeen released with no further action.
